			<div type="transcription">
				<div type="original">
					<p>The original transcription is not available.</p>
				</div>
				<div type="translation">
					<p>Confidential</p>
					<p><placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/3054643/budapest.html">Budapest</placeName>, <date when="1944-08-01">01.08.1944</date>
					</p>
					<p>[…]</p>
					<p>II. <persName ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/authorities/ehri_pers-000186">Horthy</persName> has been lately sending several letters to his <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-948" type="subject">government</term>. From his latest letter, it
						seems that he is not wholeheartedly against the <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-349" type="subject">actions</term> on the <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-351" type="subject">Jewish Question</term> in <placeName
							ref="http://www.geonames.org/719819/hungary.html">Hungary</placeName>; however, he disapproves of the <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-337" type="subject">methods</term> and cruelties that were supposedly happening during its resolution. The
						impulse for this letter came from the interventions of the <persName ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/authorities/ehri_pers-000312">Pope</persName>, the papal nuncio,Séredy and the <persName ref="#ehri_dr_king_gustaf">King of Sweden</persName>. For now, in the process of
						the <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-351" type="subject">Jewish Question</term> several categories were <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-950" type="subject">created</term>, all of which will be dealt with differently.
						In one of these categories are the <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-864" type="subject">Jews</term> of <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/2661886/kingdom-of-sweden.html">Swedish</placeName> and <placeName
							ref="http://www.geonames.org/2658434/switzerland.html">Swiss</placeName>
						<term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-1147" type="subject">nationality</term>, together about 300 – 400 people, who will be given to the <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/2661886/kingdom-of-sweden.html">Swedish</placeName> or the <placeName
							ref="http://www.geonames.org/2658434/switzerland.html">Swiss</placeName>
						<term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-948" type="subject">government</term>. In the next category are the <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-906" type="subject">Zionist</term>
						<term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-864" type="subject">Jews</term>, who are intervened for by the <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-1026" type="subject">neutral powers</term> and with help of the <placeName
							ref="http://www.geonames.org/2658434/switzerland.html">Swiss</placeName>
						<ref target="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/terezin-jewishcouncil-organisation-jmp-3754">Red Cross</ref>, there are to be brought to <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/6254930/palestine.html">Palestine</placeName>. The last category is that of the <term
							ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-803" type="subject">baptised Jews</term>, whose registration has already started and they will be dealt with differently than the other <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-864"
							type="subject">Jews</term>. However, it is very odd that the head of the state is sending letters to his <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-948" type="subject">government</term>.</p>
					<p>[…]</p>
					<p><term ref="#ehri_dr_salute_official" type="subject">Na stráž</term>!</p>
					<p><persName ref="#ehri_dr_spisiak_jan">Spišiak</persName>
					</p>
					<p/>
